=\"width:75%;height:100%;background:#EA542A;border-radius:999px;\"></div>\n                </div>\n            </div></div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#D7CBC7;margin:4px 0 0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">Real-time performance telemetry metrics sampled across production worker threads.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
